.\" shide.1 - minimal semantic CSS template
.Dd March 17, 2026
.Dt SHIDE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm shide
.Nd minimal semantic CSS template
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Pa shide.css
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
template provides responsive, accessible typography and layout
for text-oriented web pages and static documentation.
.Pp
It is small, dependency-free, and suitable for use with the
.Xr hase 1
static site generator.
.Sh FEATURES
.Bl -bullet -offset indent -compact
.It
Light and dark color support
.It
Responsive container and flexible grid system
.It
Skip links and focus-visible outlines
.El
.Sh USAGE
Include the stylesheet in your HTML:
.Bd -literal -offset indent
<link rel="stylesheet" href="shide.css">
.Ed
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr hase 1
.Sh AUTHORS
.An Sergiy Duras Aq Mt sergiy@duras.org
